Balrampur Chini Mills Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 11/11/2025 inter alia to consider and approve amongst other matters the following: 
i. Unaudited Financial Results (Standalone and Consolidated) of the Company for the half year and quarter ended 30th September 2025; 
ii. Declaration of interim dividend for the Financial Year 2025-2026 and fix record date for the same.
